   "source": [
    "### Similarity check — Synthetic vs Training vs Holdout\n",
    "\n",
    "Fidelity check of the synthetic component: an **independent generator draw** (seed 43) plays the role of the synthetic dataset; it should resemble Training about as much as Holdout does — similar distributions (PCA), and no near-zero nearest-neighbor distances (no memorization).\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 34,
   "id": "cell-064",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
